name: Collapsible.Root

disabled.description: Whether or not the collapsible is disabled. This prevents the user from interacting with it.
disabled.description_zh: Whether or not the collapsible is disabled. This prevents the user from interacting with it.

open.description: The open state of the collapsible. The content will be visible when this is true, and hidden when it's false.
open.description_zh: The open state of the collapsible. The content will be visible when this is true, and hidden when it's false.

onOpenChange.description: A callback that is fired when the collapsible's open state changes.
onOpenChange.description_zh: A callback that is fired when the collapsible's open state changes.

asChild.description: Whether to use render delegation with this component or not.
asChild.description_zh: Whether to use render delegation with this component or not.

el.description: The underlying DOM element being rendered. You can bind to this to programatically interact with the element.
el.description_zh: The underlying DOM element being rendered. You can bind to this to programatically interact with the element.

description: The root collapsible container which manages the state of the collapsible.

slots.name: builder
slots.description: The builder attributes and actions to apply to the element if using the asChild prop with delegation.
slots.description_zh: The builder attributes and actions to apply to the element if using the asChild prop with delegation.
